earish%20investors%3C%2Fa%3E%20pointed%20out%20that%20Warren%20Buffett%20is%20sitting%20on%20a%20record%20cash%20pile%20of%20%24189%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwarren-buffett-steve-hanke-berkshire-hathaway-cash-pile-stocks-recession-2024-5%5C%22%3Eimplication%2C%20according%20to%20these%20commentators%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20that%20the%20stock%20market%20is%20likely%20to%20soon%20suffer%20a%20massive%20decline%20because%20Buffett%20doesn't%20see%20any%20value%20in%20investing%20his%20firm's%20massive%20cash%20pile%20at%20the%20current%20sky-high%20valuations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20that%20couldn't%20be%20further%20from%20the%20truth%2C%20according%20to%20Chris%20Bloomstran%2C%20fund%20manager%20of%20Semper%20Augustus%2C%20which%20manages%20about%20%24550%20million%20in%20assets%20and%20counts%20Berkshire%20Hathaway%20as%20its%20largest%20position.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20recent%20interview%20with%20Business%20Insider%2C%20Bloomstran%20explained%20that%20there's%20a%20lot%20more%20nuance%20to%20Berkshire%20Hathaway's%20mountain%20of%20cash%2C%20and%20it%20doesn't%20reflect%20the%20idea%20that%20Buffett%20is%20bearish%20on%20the%20stock%20market%20or%20that%20a%20stock%20market%20crash%20is%20imminent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEverybody%20gets%20excited%2C%20they%20go%20hyperbolic%20about%20it%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20that%20big%20of%20a%20number%2C%26quot%3B%20Bloomstran%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EPutting%20Berkshire's%20cash%20pile%20into%20perspective%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20measuring%20Berkshire%20Hathaway's%20cash%20position%20on%20an%20absolute%20basis%2C%20investors%20are%20better%20off%20measuring%20the%20cash%20pile%20as%20a%20percentage%20of%20Berkshire's%20total%20assets%2C%20according%20to%20Bloomstran.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20at%2017.5%25%2C%20Berkshire%20Hathaway's%20current%20cash%20position%20is%20about%20in-line%20with%20its%20long-term%20average%20when%20measu