0insurance%20losses.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20thus%20calling%20%2482%20billion%20a%20more%20or%20less%20permanent%20cash%20reserve%2C%26quot%3B%20Bloomstran%20said%20in%20his%20annual%20investor%20letter%2C%20leaving%20about%20%24110%20billion%20available%20for%20Berkshire%20Hathaway%20to%20invest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EBerkshire%20Hathaway's%20investable%20universe%20is%20slim%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20of%20the%20massive%20size%20of%20Berkshire%20Hathaway%2C%20there's%20only%20a%20small%20group%20of%20companies%20it%20can%20invest%20in%20that%20will%20really%20move%20the%20needle%20for%20the%20conglomerate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20combine%20that%20with%20the%20fact%20that%20cash-equivalents%20like%20short-term%20Treasurys%20are%20yielding%20more%20than%205%25%2C%20Buffett%20and%20and%20his%20company%20are%20taking%20their%20time%20to%20find%20the%20right%20investment%20at%20the%20right%20price%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that%20investment%20could%20come%20at%20any%20time%2C%20just%20like%20it%20did%20in%20the%20first%20quarter%20of%202016%20when%20Berkshire%20first%20invested%20in%20Apple.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20was%20trading%20near%20record%20highs%2C%20Apple%20was%20the%20biggest%20company%20in%20the%20world%2C%20and%20Berkshire%20Hathaway's%20absolute%20cash%20pile%20was%20at%20a%20record.%20None%20of%20those%20factors%20%E2%80%94%20all%20of%20which%20are%20present%20today%20%E2%80%94%20stopped%20Buffett%20from%20making%20one%20of%20the%20best%20investments%20in%20Berkshire%20Hathaway's%20history.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe's%20limited%20to%20maybe%20the%20100%20biggest%20companies%20in%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20and%20maybe%20a%20handful%20of%20international%20businesses%20to%20be%20able%20to%20invest%20in.%20So%2C%20his%20opportunity%20set%20is%20expensive%2C%20but%20he%20doesn't%20mind%20earning%205.3%25%20in%20the%20interim%2C%20but%20it%20does%20not%20mean%20in%20any%20way%2C%20shape%2C%20or%20form%20that%20a%20stock%20market%20crash%20is%20imminent.%20He's%20just%20trying%20to%20find%20great%20prices%20stable%20enough%20to%20put%20money%20to%20work.%20His%20universe%20is%20limited%2C%26quot%3B%20Bloomstran%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPut%20together%2C%20investors%20shouldn't%20have%20a%20bearish%20view%20on%20the%20stock%20market%20just%20because%20Berkshire%20Hathaway%20is%20sitting%20on%20a%20record%20pile%20of%20cash.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETake%20it%20from%20Buffett%20himself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20%26quot%3Bwhat%20is%20Buffett%20waiting%20for%3F%26quot%3B%20with%20regards%20to%20Berkshire's%20cash%20pile%20at%20this%20year's%20annual%20shareholder%20meeting%2C%20the%20legendary%20investor%20responded%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20only%20swing%20at%20pitches%20we%20like.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwarren-buffett-record-cash-pile-stock-market-crash-signal-berkshire-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716034561000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F608fe7c634af8d001859a7d1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fwarren-buffett-record-cash-pile-stock-market-crash-signal-berkshire-2024-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BEverybody%20gets%20excited%2C%20they%20go%20hyperbolic%20about%20it%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20that%20big%20of%20a%20number%2C%26quot%3B%20Chris%20Bloomstran%20said%20of%20Buffett's%20%24189%20billion%20cash%20pile.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mfox%40businessinsider.com%20(Matthew%20Fox)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fwarren-buffett-record-cash-pile-stock-market-crash-signal-berkshire-2024-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20used%20Amazon%20Showroom%20to%20design%20my%20office.%20The%20under-the-radar%20