%2C%20can%20suck%20sperm%20into%20needles%20and%20place%20them%20into%20eggs.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20cofounders%20say%20automation%20will%20challenge%20an%20industry%20rife%20with%20arbitrary%20decision-making.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ENormally%2C%20in-vitro%20fertilization%2C%20or%20IVF%2C%20is%20a%20manual%20affair.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20doctor%20performs%20a%20small%20surgery%2C%20places%20the%20patient's%20eggs%20in%20a%20test%20tube%2C%20and%20passes%20the%20tube%20through%20a%20little%20window%20to%20a%20lab%2C%20where%20a%20scientist%20combines%20them%20with%20sperm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20small%20clinic%20in%20Guadalajara%2C%20Mexico%2C%20the%20process%20is%20radically%20different.%20Once%20that%20test%20tube%20makes%20it%20through%20the%20window%2C%20it's%20handed%20over%20to%20robots%20backed%20by%20a%20vast%20AI%20infrastructure.%20There%2C%20a%20startup%20called%20Conceivable%20Life%20Sciences%20is%20automating%20the%20IVF%20lab%20from%20start%20to%20finish.%20The%20scientists%20kick%20back%20and%20supervise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConceivable%20imagines%20its%20IVF%20labs%20all%20around%20the%20world%2C%20each%20containing%20lines%20of%20shiny%20white%20boxes%20working%20together%20in%20untouched%20harmony.%20For%20now%2C%20its%20work%20is%20limited%20to%20small%20studies%20and%20robotic%20prototypes.%20But%20the%20prototypes%20are%20working%2C%20according%20to%20Conceivable's%20data%2C%20interviews%2C%20and%20videos%20shared%20with%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20push%20of%20a%20button%20or%20two%2C%20Conceivable's%20robots%20immobilize%20sperm%20with%20lasers%3B%20suck%20them%20into%20needles%3B%20insert%20them%20into%20eggs%20they've%20plucked%20from%20bloody%20fluid%3B%20and%2C%20after%20incubation%2C%20give%20the%20resulting%20embryos%20free%20rides%20on%20a%20microscopic%20tennis%20racket%20into%20vials%20of%20liquid%20nitrogen%2C%20freezing%20them%20faster%20than%20you%20can%20blink.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22In%20Conceivable's%20automated%20lab%2C%20robots%20use%20a%20microscopic%20tennis%20racket%20to%20dunk%20embryos%20into%20fluid.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6644e2319686a6f37b003862%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22782%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIn%20Conceivable's%20automated%20lab%2C%20robots%20use%20a%20microscopic%20tennis%20racket%20to%20dunk%20pre-embryos%20into%20fluid.%3Cp%3EConceivable%20Life%20Sciences%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEleven%20women%20so%20far%20have%20become%20pregnant%20with%20help%20from%20one%20or%20more%20of%20these%20Conceivable%20robots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlong%20the%20way%2C%20the%20company%20says%20it%20has%20achieved%20several%20breakthroughs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20months%2C%20Conceivable%20became%20the%20first%20company%20to%20robotically%20perform%20intracytoplasmic%20sperm%20injection%20(ICSI%20or%20%26quot%3Bicksee%26quot%3B)%2C%20the%20delicate%20process%20by%20which%20a%20sperm%20is%20placed%20inside%20an%20egg%2C%20according%20to%20Conceivable%20and%20video%20footage%20shared%20with%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20December%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.conceivable.life%2Fjacques-cohen%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efamed%3C%2Fa%3E%20embryologist%20Jacques%20Cohen%2C%20Conceivable's%20chief%20scientific%20officer%2C%20steered%20the%20robots%20through%20ICSI%20with%20his%20keyboard%20and%20mouse.%20The%20procedure%20was%20in%20Mexico%3B%20Cohen%20was%20in%20New%20York%20City%20sitting%20at%20his%20desk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20embryo%20was%20transferred%20on%20February%2023%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20pregnancy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20doing%20transcontinental%20ICSIs%20all%20the%20time%20now%2C%20making%20them%20routine%2C%26quot%3B%20Joshua%20Abram%2C%20Conceivable's%20co-CEO%20and%20cofounder%2C%20told%20BI%20in%20an%20interview.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20the%20first%20company%20in%20the%20world%20to%20have%20ever%20done%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20robots%20can%20now%20perform%20ICSI%20autonomously%2C%20another%20%26quot%3Bworld's%20first%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20Abram.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20ultrasound%20of%20the%20embryo%20created%20by%20Conceivable's%20first%20remote%20ICSI.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6646916620abc1efe8fad315%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22338%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20ultrasound%20of%20the%20embryo%20created%20by%20Conceivable's%20first%20remote%20ICSI.%3Cp%3EConceivable%20Life%20Sciences%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22515f54e5-47b5-4782-88ec-e9f5a19999d4%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BNo%20baby%2C%20no%20fee%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20IVF%20demand%20is%20surging%2C%20despite%20the%20treatment%20being%20slow%2C%20uncertain%2C%20and%20expensive.%20Millions%20of%20women%20live%20in%20places%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.asrm.org%2Fpractice-guidance%2Fethics-opinions%2Fdisparities-in-access-to-effective-treatment-for-infertility-in-the-united-states-an-ethics-committee-opinion-2021%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewithout%20infertility%20centers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20the%20clinical%20experts%20who%20run%20them%20are%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Farticles%2Fprivate-equitys-bet-on-fertility-focuses-on-sectors-staffing-shortages-e6bfae2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshort%20supply%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Plus%2C%20it's%20punitively%20expensive.%20In%20the%20US%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdbsable.medium.com%2Fhaving-an-ivf-baby-vs-buying-a-toyota-847a834c3b52%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIVF%20costs%20as%20much%20as%20a%20new%20car%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20usually%20has%20to%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Freproductiverights.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F02%2F64785006_Infertility-and-IVF-Access-in-the-U.S.-Fact-Sheet_2.5.2020_Final.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erepeated%3C%2Fa%3E%20before%20it%20works.%20For%20many%20patients%2C%20this%20can%20mean%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsbivf.com%2Ffuture-family-fertility-financing%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eborrowing%20heavily%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20if%20they're%20lucky%20enough%20to%20have%20a%20good%20credit%20score.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20economy%2C%20robots%20have%20taken%20on%20a%20range%20of%20assignments%2C%20from%20moving%20product%20in%20Amazon%20warehouses%20to%20helping%20surgeons%20perform%20minimally%20invasive%20surgeries.%20That's%20made%20goods%20and%20services%20more%20available%20and%20cheaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConceivable%2C%20which%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flist-top-healthcare-startups-investors-take-off-in-2024%23conceivable-life-sciences-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eraised%3C%2Fa%3E%20%2420%20million%20in%20venture%20capital%2C%20is%20betting%20that%20robots%20are%20ready%20for%20IVF%2C%20too.%20Automation%2C%20the%20cofounders%20argue%2C%20will%20offer%20more%20dexterity%20in%20handling%20microscopic%20cells%20than%20shaky%20human%20hands%20fumbling%20with%20pipettes.%20Plus%2C%20it%20should%20collapse%20costs%3B%20the%20startup%20plans%20to%20charge%20most%20patients%20%2415%2C000%20for%20IVF%2C%20and%20only%20when%20it%20works%2C%C2%A0potentially%20saving%20patients%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20dollars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20baby%2C%20no%20fee%2C%26quot%3B%20Abram%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20interviews%20with%20BI%2C%20experts%20in%20the%20field%20were%20skeptical%20of%20Conceivable's%20plans%2C%20but%20not%20dismissive.%20Many%20like%20Dr.%20Lora%20Shahine%2C%20a%20fertility%20physician%20based%20in%20Seattle%2C%20believe%20automation%20could%20help%20the%20supply-demand%20mismatch%20that%20constrains%20care%20for%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.who.int%2Fnews%2Fitem%2F04-04-2023-1-in-6-people-globally-affected-by-infertility%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprevalent%20disease%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20it%20must%20be%20done%20without%20compromising%20success%20rates%20and%20patient%20care%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Conceivable's%20future%20IVF%20lab.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6644e2d3f27898f532d7fdf7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EConceivable's%20future%20IVF%20lab.%3Cp%3EConceivable%20Life%20Sciences%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2239493c75-af32-4969-8a63-8cf2eeffaa2f%5C%22%3EIVF's%20tole%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFertility%20care%20as%20it%20stands%20today%20can%20be%20just%20as%20terrifying%20as%20the%20notion%20of%20babies%20created%20with%20robots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202014%2C%20Emma%20wasn't%20looking%20to%20have%20kids.%20But%20a%20blood%20test%20showed%20she%20had%20limited%20time.%20She%20felt%20pushed%20into%20IVF%2C%20during%20which%20her%20relationship%20buckled%20and%20broke%20from%20the%20strain%20of%20a%20miscarriage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEmma%20had%20to%20make%20an%20arbitrary%20choice%2C%20based%20on%20not-enough%20information%2C%20from%20a%20dizzying%20cast%20of%20providers%2C%20she%20told%20BI.%20Implant%20the%20eggs%20now%3F%20Or%20save%20them%20for%20later%3F%20When%20is%20later%3F%20What%20if%20you%20meet%20someone%20else%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThen%2C%20do%20you%20want%20to%20save%20the%20eggs%20so%20they%20can%20fertilize%20them%2C%20or%20do%20you%20want%20to%20have%20the%20knowledge%20that%20you%20have%20viable%20embryos%3F%26quot%3B%20Emma%20said%20of%20her%20thinking%20at%20the%20time.%20(She%20asked%20to%20be%20referred%20to%20by%20a%20different%20name%20to%20keep%20her%20health%20history%20private.%20BI%20knows%20her%20identity).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202016%2C%20Emma%20froze%20her%20eggs%20and%20walked%20away%20from%20the%20unwanted%20role%20of%20being%20a%20project%20manager%20of%20her%20own%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20she%20was%20working%20for%20Abram%20and%20Alan%20Murray%2C%20his%20longtime%20business%20partner.%20One%20day%2C%20the%20three%20of%20them%20got%20to%20talking%20about%20opportunities%20for%20startups%20in%20the%20healthcare%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20then%20I%20remember%20saying%2C%20'Well%2C%20here's%20a%20sector%20you%20might%20want%20to%20consider%2C'%26quot%3B%20Emma%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2268f13b60-00c5-43bb-8741-bbe9ce5df2b1%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BMilk%20jugs%26quot%3B%20and%20a%20Catholic%20Eucharist%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETroubled%20by%20her%20experience%2C%20Abram%20and%20Murray%20started%20visiting%20IVF%20labs%20in%202017.%20The%20lack%20of%20automation%20astounded%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20their%20travels%2C%20%26quot%3Bmilk%20jugs%26quot%3B%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.labrepco.com%2Fproduct%2Fxt21-ai-animal-insemination-cryogenic-system-with-6-5-canisters-1122-x-1-2cc-straws%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elow-tech%3C%2Fa%3E%20cryogenic%20storage%20tanks)%2C%20sticky%20notes%2C%20and%20sharpie%20markers%20were%20being%20used%20to%20locate%2C%20label%2C%20and%20store%20eggs%20and%20embryos%2C%20they%20told%20BI.%20People%20with%20extensive%20vocational%20training%20%E2%80%94%20embryologists%20who%20oversee%20the%20lab%20portion%20of%20IVF%20%E2%80%94%20were%20spending%20much%20of%20their%20time%20squishing%20little%20drops%20out%20of%20pipettes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20one%20visit%20to%20a%20premier%20lab%2C%20the%20scene%20was%20reminiscent%20of%20a%20Catholic%20Eucharist%3A%20Everyone%20was%20holding%20specimens%20with%20such%20delicacy%20while%20trying%20not%20to%20bump%20into%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20kept%20seeing%20those%20milk%20jugs%20pop%20up.%20Milk%20jugs%20underneath%20desks%2C%20milk%20jugs%20underneath%20stairways%2C%20milk%20jugs%20in%20the%20hallways%2C%20milk%20jugs%20in%20rooms%2C%26quot%3B%20Murray%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20kept%20looking%20for%20the%20wires.%20How%20are%20they%20connected%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLittle%20drop%2C%20little%20drop%2C%20little%20drop%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BHandwriting%20on%20the%20back%20of%20Petri%20dishes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20they%20founded%20TMRW%20Life%20Sciences%2C%20which%20makes%20a%20kind%20of%20futuristic%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftmrwlifesciences.com%2Four-technology%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EATM%20machine%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20stores%20eggs%20and%20embryos%20more%20securely.%20The%20following%20year%2C%20Abram%20and%20Murray%20set%20their%20sights%20on%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20IVF%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20a%20big%20push%20on%20the%20part%20of%20pharmaceutical%20and%20life%20sciences%20companies%20to%20automate%20labs.%20Robots%20were%20improving%20while%20research%20needs%2C%20such%20as%20using%20genetic%20insights%20to%20make%20new%20drugs%2C%20were%20getting%20more%20complicated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECurious%20about%20how%20it%20all%20worked%2C%20the%20pair%20toured%20the%20San%20Francisco%20lab%20of%20biotech%20company%20Invitae%2C%20where%20it%20processes%20DNA%20samples.%20The%2050%2C000-square-foot%20facility%20was%20stuffed%20with%20robots.%20Conveyor%20belts%20moved%20trays%20of%20test%20tubes.%20Robots%20extracted%20droplets%20from%20the%20tubes%20and%20put%20them%20onto%20chips%20that%20rode%20into%20DNA-ciphering%20machines.%20There%20were%20only%20about%20three%20people%20helping%20move%20the%20process%20along%2C%20Murray%20recalled.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20was%20a%20partial%20aha%20moment%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20whole%20other%20world%20outside%20of%20IVF%20that's%20figured%20out%20how%20to%20use%20robotics.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20trip%2C%20Murray%20attended%20lab-automation%20trade%20shows%2C%20walking%20from%20booth%20to%20booth%20for%20days%20at%20a%20time.%20When%20a%20piece%20of%20equipment%20had%20a%20potential%20use%20in%20fertility%20care%2C%20he%20wrote%20it%20down%20%E2%80%94%20eventually%20forming%20a%20kind%20of%20shopping%20list%20for%20the%20IVF%20lab%20of%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225120%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Joshua%20Abram%20and%20Alan%20Murray.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6647634a20abc1efe8faf43a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222880%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJoshua%20Abram%20and%20Alan%20Murray.%3Cp%3EConceivable%20Life%20Sciences%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2217a09a7e-6974-430c-bf4e-94b49064c1af%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EFrom%20prayer%20to%20AI%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHalf%20a%20continent%20away%2C%20a%20physician%20was%20growing%20frustrated%20by%20the%20constraints%20of%20his%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDr.%20Alejandro%20Ch%C3%A1vez-Badiola%20became%20a%20reproductive%20endocrinology%20and%20infertility%20(REI)%20doctor%2C%20the%20kind%20that%20oversees%20IVF%2C%20because%20he%20was%20drawn%20to%20the%20idea%20of%20helping%20families%20reach%20their%20happiest%20moments.%20Every%20time%20he%20performed%20an%20embryo%20transfer%2C%20he%20prayed%3A%20%26quot%3BLet%20it%20be%20a%20good%20person.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20training%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20he%20opened%20his%20first%20clinic%20in%20Guadalajara%2C%20hoping%20to%20make%20an%20impact%20in%20his%20hometown.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20things%20went%20wrong%2C%20he%20wanted%20to%20know%20why.%20But%20some%20of%20the%20most%20crucial%20decisions%20in%20IVF%20occurred%20beyond%20the%20wall%20separating%20his%20clinic%20from%20the%20lab.%20He%20had%20a%20trustworthy%20team%20of%20embryologists%2C%20but%20US%20clinics%20kept%20poaching%20them%2C%20and%20the%20tools%20at%20their%20disposal%20were%20limited.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20year%2C%20when%20one%20of%20the%20physician's%20healthier%2C%20younger%20patients%20didn't%20get%20pregnant%20after%20two%20IVF%20cycles%2C%20he%20called%20a%20meeting%20with%20staff%20to%20ask%20about%20the%20quality%20of%20her%20eggs%20and%20embryos.%20To%20his%20frustration%2C%20they%20said%20they%20were%20%26quot%3Bbeautiful.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGuys%2C%20come%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20Ch%C3%A1vez-Badiola%20replied.%20%26quot%3BThe%20patient%20is%20not%20getting%20pregnant.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20goal%20of%20making%20moments%20like%20this%20more%20scientific%2C%20the%20young%20doctor%20started%20working%20with%20professors%2C%20mathematicians%2C%20and%20engineers%20to%20put%20artificial%20intelligence%20to%20use%20in%20IVF.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20trained%20one%20AI%20model%20to%20rank%20sperm%20based%20on%20insights%20from%20real%20patient%20data.%20During%20fertilization%2C%20his%20embryologists%20usually%20picked%20out%20good-enough-looking%20swimmers%20from%20the%20Petri%20dish%20that%20were%20close%20to%20the%20needle.%20Now%2C%20the%20computer%20told%20them%20which%20ones%20to%20select%20based%20on%20movement%20patterns%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F35989168%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eassociated%20with%20the%20creation%20of%20embryos%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20he%20was%20running%20into%20another%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20didn't%20matter%20if%20Ch%C3%A1vez-Badiola's%20AI%20could%20find%20the%20best%20sperm%20if%20a%20human%20couldn't%20reliably%20catch%20it.%20A%20typical%20droplet%20contains%20thousands%20of%20sperm.%20The%20right%20one%20could%20swim%20out%20of%20view%20of%20the%20microscope%2C%20or%20get%20squished.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20physician%20needed%20robotic%20assistance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225760%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Conceivable's%20cofounders%2C%20Joshua%20Abram%2C%20Dr.%20Alejandro%20Ch%C3%A1vez-Badiola%2C%20and%20Alan%20Murray.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6644eb4a14fb5b23cc5caed5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223840%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EConceivable's%20cofounders%2C%20Joshua%20Abram%2C%20Dr.%20Alejandro%20Ch%C3%A1vez-Badiola%2C%20and%20Alan%20Murray.%3Cp%3EConceivable%20Life%20Sciences%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221a4af987-86c1-4bf6-a86e-ed161ae3a716%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20meeting%20of%20the%20minds%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThanks%20to%20COVID-19%2C%20Ch%C3%A1vez-Badiola%20got%20his%20chance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20March%202020%2C%20when%20the%20pandemic%20ended%20travel%20to%20the%20US%2C%20Ch%C3%A1vez-Badiola%20found%20himself%20stranded%20in%20London%20with%20Murray%20and%20Abram.%20Having%20run%20into%20each%20other%20before%20in%20IVF%20circles%2C%20they%20met%20at%20the%20bar%20of%20the%20Langham%20Hotel%2C%20where%20the%20conversation%20turned%20to%20the%20sorry%20state%20of%20the%20fertility%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20discussed%20how%20aging%20maternal%20populations%2C%20declining%20sperm%20counts%2C%20and%20other%20factors%20had%20increased%20demand%20for%20IVF.%20But%20the%20supply%20side%20had%20not%20responded.%20There%20are%20just%20north%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fertstert.org%2Farticle%2FS0015-0282(23)00780-X%2Ffulltext%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E1%2C000%20REIs%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20US%3B%20competition%20for%20embryologists%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2F%3Freload%3Dtrue%26_%3D1715109330096%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efierce%3C%2Fa%3E%3B%20and%20their%20existing%20manual%20process%20is%20slow.%20A%20standard%20IVF%20operation%20may%20struggle%20to%20retrieve%20eggs%20from%205-10%20patients%20in%20a%20day%2C%20according%20to%20BI%20interviews%20with%20independent%20fertility%20doctors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat's%20more%2C%20on%20average%2C%20women%20have%20to%20undergo%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hhs.gov%2Fabout%2Fnews%2F2024%2F03%2F13%2Ffact-sheet-in-vitro-fertilization-ivf-use-across-united-states.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etwo%20or%20three%3C%2Fa%3E%20IVF%20cycles%20to%20get%20pregnant.%20But%20AI%20and%20automation%2C%20which%20could%20hypothetically%20improve%20success%20rates%2C%20aren't%20prominent.%20In%20a%20typical%20clinic%2C%20embryos%20are%20removed%20from%20the%20incubator%20in%20batches%20according%20to%20human%20schedules%2C%20not%20when%20best%20suits%20the%20individual%20embryos%3B%20robotics%20could%20change%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Langham%20meeting%20kicked%20off%20a%20two-year%20conversation%20in%20which%20Abram%2C%20Murray%2C%20and%20Ch%C3%A1vez-Badiola%20rethought%20IVF%20from%20the%20ground-up%2C%20steadily%20convincing%20themselves%20that%20automation%20on%20a%20grand%20scale%20was%20possible.%20In%202022%2C%20emboldened%20by%20robotics%20and%20AI%20gains%20in%20other%20industries%2C%20they%20founded%20Conceivable%20to%20prove%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Conceivable's%20cofounders%20tinker%20with%20an%20applied%20optics%20lab.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66469dcc9fc063e829b215b6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EConceivable's%20cofounders%20tinker%20with%20an%20applied%20optics%20lab.%3Cp%3ECh%C3%A1vez-Badiola%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22554dbfe3-2a57-4509-90f3-3cec783fd798%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EInspiration%20from%20chip%20manufacturing%20and%20Tesla%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20task%20at%20hand%20was%20building%20robots%20and%20AI%20capable%20of%20handling%20the%20five%20stages%20of%20an%20IVF%20lab%3A%20egg%20preparation%2C%20sperm%20selection%2C%20fertilization%2C%20incubation%2C%20and%20freezing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20hardware%2C%20Conceivable%20turned%20to%20the%20microscopic%20worlds%20of%20chip%20manufacturing%20and%20lab%20automation%2C%20buying%20motors%20that%20allow%20its%20roughly%2020%20robots%20to%20move%20by%20increments%20as%20small%20as%20five%20millionths%20of%20a%20millimeter%2C%20plus%20sensors%20and%20tiny%20tools.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20software%2C%20Conceivable%20took%20inspiration%20from%20the%20likes%20of%20Tesla.%20Its%20core%20%26quot%3Bobject-recognition%26quot%3B%20AI%20systems%20are%20the%20same%20used%20in%20self-driving%20cars%2C%20but%20trained%20on%20images%20of%20sperm%20and%20eggs%20instead%20of%20stop-signs%20and%20pedestrians.%20They%20tell%20the%20robots%20where%20to%20move%20and%20how%20far%2C%20based%20on%20data%20from%20microscopes%2C%2030%20times%20a%20second.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20doesn't%20matter%20if%20you're%20taking%20a%20picture%20of%20the%20highway%20from%20the%20front%20of%20a%20car%20or%20an%20egg%20through%20the%20lens%20of%20a%20microscope%2C%26quot%3B%20Brian%20Bixon%2C%20Conceivable's%20head%20of%20product%2C%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BThe%20first-principle%20thinking%20is%20the%20same.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20while%2C%20the%20robots%20practiced%20on%20hamster%20and%20rabbit%20eggs%20in%20Conceivable's%20office%20in%20Guadalajara.%20Then%20engineers%20gradually%20introduced%20them%20into%20Ch%C3%A1vez-Badiola's%20clinic%20six%20blocks%20down%20the%20street%20for%20a%20clinical%20study.%20Fifty%20hopeful%20patients%20with%20infertility%2C%20whose%20care%20is%20overseen%20by%20other%20doctors%2C%20volunteered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20has%20mostly%20tested%20the%20robots%20working%20in%20isolated%20IVF%20processes%2C%20including%2C%20lately%2C%20ICSI.%20The%20machines%20originally%20tackled%20ICSI%20in%20about%2020%20steps%2C%20each%20allowing%20for%20interventions.%20%26quot%3BWe'd%20stop%2C%20look%2C%20hit%20the%20next%20go%20button%2C%20stop%2C%20look%2C%26quot%3B%20Murray%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20December%2C%20the%20team%20has%20been%20carefully%20linking%20the%20steps%20together%2C%20with%20the%20goal%20of%20full%20robotic%20autonomy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228448%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Conceivable%20Life%20Sciences%20team.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66469a8620abc1efe8fad33d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%226336%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Conceivable%20Life%20Sciences%20team.%3Cp%3EConceivable%20Life%20Sciences%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229c247ffb-aeb3-4455-b98f-3bb3ba767cc9%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAutomating%20conception%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20March%206%2C%20Conceivable%20had%20a%20rocket-launch%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20morning%2C%20eggs%20from%20three%20patients%20were%20retrieved%20and%20passed%20through%20the%20little%20window%20between%20the%20clinic%20and%20the%20lab%20in%20Guadalajara.%20The%20tube%20of%20fluid%20was%20poured%20into%20a%20dish%2C%20which%20Conceivable's%20AI%20system%20scanned%20for%20eggs%20with%20a%20technology%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fbooks%2FNBK554044%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erenders%3C%2Fa%3E%20images%20in%203-D.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22640%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20view%20of%20an%20egg%20via%20Conceivable's%20most%20expensive%20microscope.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6646a24a20abc1efe8fad373%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20view%20of%20an%20egg%20via%20Conceivable's%20most%20expensive%20microscope.%3Cp%3EConceivable%20Life%20Sciences%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20afternoon%2C%20half%20the%20eggs%20went%20to%20human%20embryologists.%20The%20other%20half%20went%20to%20Conceivable's%20setup%2C%20and%20the%20first%20egg%20was%20placed%2C%20along%20with%20a%20droplet%20of%20sperm%2C%20on%20a%202x2%20inch%20square.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20square%20was%20situated%20underneath%20two%20needles%2C%20each%20held%20by%20a%20petite%2C%20four-axis%20robot.%20One%20handled%20the%20sperm%3B%20the%20other%2C%20the%20egg.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20push%20of%20a%20green%20button%20on%20a%20touchscreen%2C%20the%20robots%20went%20about%20automating%20conception.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20lab%2C%20there%20were%20two%20engineers%20and%20two%20embryologists.%20Video%20footage%20was%20simulcast%20to%20more%20experts%2C%20who%20whispered%20commentary%20like%20golf%20announcers%2C%20and%20Conceivable%20employees%20around%20the%20world%2C%20who%20huddled%20around%20screens.%20It%20felt%20like%20a%20%26quot%3Brocket%20launch%2C%26quot%3B%20recalled%20Murray%2C%20who%20traveled%20to%20Guadalajara%20for%20the%20occasion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFirst%20came%20sperm%20selection.%20An%20AI-guided%20laser%20underneath%20the%20square%20was%20supposed%20to%20zap%20the%20best%20one.%20In%20this%20case%2C%20it%20shot%20the%20swimmer%20%26quot%3Ba%20little%20toward%20the%20midsection%2C%26quot%3B%20Murray%20said.%20Oops.%20They%20went%20with%20a%20lucky%20runner-up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20second%20sperm%20was%20immobilized%2C%20one%20of%20the%20robots%20sucked%20it%20inside%20a%20needle%2C%20tail-first.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENext%2C%20the%20other%20robot%20moved%20its%20needle%20close%20to%20the%20egg%20and%20used%20suction%20to%20hold%20it%20in%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20AI-guided%20laser%20shot%20a%20wedge%20out%20of%20the%20egg's%20outermost%20membrane%20to%20clear%20an%20easier%20path%20for%20the%20sperm.%20Once%20the%20sperm%20needle%20was%20hovering%20right%20at%20the%20egg's%20midpoint%2C%20the%20first%20robot%20used%20%26quot%3Bfluid%20dynamics%26quot%3B%20and%20other%20technical%20know-how%20to%20position%20the%20sperm%20at%20the%20very%20tip%2C%20Murray%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAre%20you%20ready%20to%20inject%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20computer%20asked%20the%20humans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Conceivable's%20AI%20zaps%20a%20sperm.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66469fc620abc1efe8fad363%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22338%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EConceivable's%20AI%20zaps%20a%20sperm.%3Cp%3EConceivable%20Life%20Sciences%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f78a7e20-8665-4d85-8e92-895a860afb11%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20first%20%26quot%3Bembryoneer%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20answer%20was%20yes.%20So%20Gerardo%20Mendizabal-Ruiz%2C%20a%20top%20Conceivable%20engineer%20and%20VP%2C%20pushed%20the%20green%20button%20while%20everyone%20held%20their%20breath.%20(Colleagues%20now%20call%20him%20the%20first%20%26quot%3Bembryoneer.%26quot%3B)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20electrical%20signal%20vibrated%20a%20crystal%20motor%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20needle%20holding%20the%20sperm%2C%20which%20helped%20a%20tiny%20blade%20more%20easily%20cut%20into%20the%20egg's%20membrane.%20The%20needle%20went%20in%2C%20but%20not%20too%20far%3A%20Six%20algorithms%20prevented%20it%20from%20piercing%20the%20egg's%20other%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20using%20a%20little%20puff%20of%20air%2C%20the%20robot%20discharged%20the%20sperm%20and%20retracted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Conceivable's%20automated%20ICSI%2C%20sped%20up%20for%20effect.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6646489614fb5b23cc5d4e72%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22338%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EConceivable's%20automated%20ICSI%2C%20sped%20up%20for%20effect.%3Cp%3EConceivable%20Life%20Sciences%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EApplause%20erupted%20over%20Zoom%20and%20around%20Murray%2C%20who%20watched%20the%20broadcast%20with%20Conceivable%20engineers%20down%20the%20street.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECh%C3%A1vez-Badiola%20felt%20the%20tension%20dissipate%2C%20comparing%20the%20moment%20to%20watching%20his%20oldest%20son%20walk%20for%20the%20first%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConceivable%20repeated%20the%20process%20until%20it%20created%20five%20would-be%20embryos%2C%20from%2012%20eggs%20in%20total%2C%20slightly%20outperforming%20the%20human%20embryologists%2C%20Murray%20and%20Bixon%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20embryos%20led%20to%20a%20successful%20pregnancy%20for%20a%20patient%20in%20April.%20Carla%20Patricia%20Barragan%20%C3%81lvarez%2C%20a%20Conceivable%20biologist%2C%20taped%20a%20picture%20of%20it%20to%20a%20whiteboard%2C%20where%20she%20keeps%20a%20personal%20tally%20of%20Conceivable%20pregnancies%2C%20like%20relatives%20on%20a%20fridge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFully%20automatic%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20description%20reads.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22642%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Carla%20Patricia%20Barragan%20%C3%81lvarez%2C%20an%20experimental%20biologist%20at%20Conceivable%2C%20keeps%20a%20personal%20tally%20of%20the%20startup's%20pregnancies.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66467edf14fb5b23cc5d7eea%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22482%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECarla%20Patricia%20Barragan%20%C3%81lvarez%2C%20an%20experimental%20biologist%20at%20Conceivable%2C%20keeps%20a%20personal%20tally%20of%20the%20startup's%20pregnancies.%3Cp%3EConceivable%20Life%20Sciences%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220c61a1ea-a5e0-4780-a826-69955cde08e3%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20new%20test%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EConceivable%20has%20a%20long%20road%20ahead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Guadalajara%2C%20the%20new%20instruments%20have%20improved%20enough%20to%20perform%20above%20industry%20standards%2C%20according%20to%20the%20startup.%20But%20they've%20largely%20not%20been%20put%20to%20the%20test%20as%20a%20full%20ensemble.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20September%2C%20Conceivable%20plans%20to%20launch%20another%20clinical%20study%20in%20Mexico%20City%2C%20enrolling%20250%20patients%20from%20a%20nearby%20hospital.%20Similar%20to%20the%20Guadalajara%20effort%2C%20half%20their%20eggs%20will%20go%20through%20a%20conventional%20lab%2C%20while%20the%20other%20half%20go%20to%20Conceivable%20robots.%20This%20time%2C%20though%2C%20the%20robots%20will%20automate%20every%20IVF%20process%20for%20every%20specimen%2C%20end-to-end.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConceivable%20will%20mainly%20be%20looking%20for%20how%20many%20embryos%20it%20can%20produce%20from%2010%20eggs.%20The%20higher%20the%20ratio%2C%20the%20fewer%20cycles%20of%20IVF%20are%20required%20for%20patients.%20The%20startup%20intends%20to%20publish%20the%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b569e95b-90a4-4e08-9c5f-0ffb23be4845%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EPlugging%20into%20the%20system%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20proving%20the%20technology%20is%20only%20step%20one.%20In%20healthcare%2C%20a%20greater%20challenge%20for%20companies%20can%20be%20plugging%20into%20the%20existing%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20short%20term%2C%20Conceivable%20plans%20to%20work%20with%20existing%20IVF%20providers%20to%20provide%20an%20alternative%20to%20their%20labs.%20With%20private-equity%20buying%20up%20IVF%20clinics%2C%20Conceivable%20will%20make%20a%20bid%20to%20help%20these%20investors%20boost%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20thought%20the%20large%20PE-backed%20incumbents%20would%20be%20hostile%2C%26quot%3B%20Abram%20said.%20%26quot%3BIn%20fact%2C%20they're%20coming%20to%20us%20and%20asking%20to%20partner.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELonger-term%2C%20Conceivable%20plans%20to%20run%20independent%20labs%20in%20partnership%20with%20OBGYNs%2C%20who%20would%20oversee%20patient%20care%20leading%20up%20to%20the%20egg%20retrieval%20and%20lab%20work.%20REIs%20employed%20by%20Conceivable%20would%20oversee%20these%20cases%2C%20intervene%20when%20needed%2C%20and%20perform%20the%20surgeries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222f36ddd4-15c9-47a9-a93c-845f23f6284a%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHot-button%20issue%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOBGYNs%20aren't%20trained%20in%20the%20bulk%20of%20fertility%20care.%20Involving%20them%20more%20is%20a%20hot-button%20issue%20in%20the%20REI%20community%2C%20according%20to%20Dr.%20Eduardo%20Hariton%2C%20a%20fertility%20physician%20and%20executive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20REIs%20aren't%20meeting%20demand.%20The%20community%2C%20therefore%2C%20should%20take%20the%20lead%20on%20designing%20frameworks%20for%20this%20kind%20of%20collaboration%20before%20the%20market%20beats%20them%20to%20it%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20need%20to%20have%20very%20clear%20guidelines%20about%20what%20the%20scope%20of%20practice%20is%2C%26quot%3B%20Hariton%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20regulatory%20hurdles%2C%20Conceivable's%20path%20might%20be%20more%20straightforward.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fertility%20industry%20is%20more%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fhealth%2F2024%2F04%2F28%2Fivf-errors-fertility-clinics-regulation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eself-policed%3C%2Fa%3E%20than%20other%20areas%20of%20healthcare.%20Since%20the%20startup%20doesn't%20aim%20to%20sell%20equipment%20for%20other%20people%20to%20use%2C%20it%20would%20largely%20fall%20under%20the%20same%20regulatory%20scheme%20as%20lab%20companies%20LabCorp%20and%20Quest%20Diagnostics%2C%20Murray%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20all%20goes%20to%20plan%2C%20Conceivable%20thinks%20it%20could%20be%20running%20labs%20as%20soon%20as%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fconceivable-automating-ivf-fertility-robots-ai-startup-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716033602000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F664528967415a05fdd08c079%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fconceivable-automating-ivf-fertility-robots-ai-startup-2024-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Conceivable%20Life%20Sciences%20is%20automating%20IVF%20labs%20to%20make%20fertility%20care%20less%20arbitrary.%20Its%20r