3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20to%20play%20that%20balancing%20game%20between%20what%20is%20inside%20your%20rucksack%20and%20on%20your%20person%20versus%20what%20can%20be%20delivered%20later%20is%20a%20very%20fun%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D3I7dMfNRz7A%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echallenging%20game%20in%20the%20Arctic%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d51f5ad7-80f4-436c-9fad-23bf3c24015e%5C%22%3ECan't%20miss%20anything%20that%20would%20injure%20a%20jumper%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22U.S.%20Army%20paratroopers%20from%203rd%20Battalion%2C%20509th%20Parachute%20Infantry%20Regiment%2C%202nd%20Infantry%20Brigade%20Combat%20Team%20(Airborne)%2C%2011th%20Airborne%20Division%2C%20leave%20the%20drop%20zone%20after%20finishing%20an%20airborne%20operation%20as%20part%20of%20Joint%20Pacific%20Multinational%20Readiness%20Center%2024-02%20in%20Donnelly%20Training%20Area%2C%20Alaska%2C%20Feb.%208%2C%202024.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65d9050a90413ab8e1d68f2d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EU.S.%20Army%20paratroopers%20from%203rd%20Battalion%2C%20509th%20Parachute%20Infantry%20Regiment%2C%202nd%20Infantry%20Brigade%20Combat%20Team%20(Airborne)%2C%2011th%20Airborne%20Division%2C%20leave%20the%20drop%20zone%20after%20finishing%20an%20airborne%20operation%20as%20part%20of%20Joint%20Pacific%20Multinational%20Readiness%20Center%2024-02%20in%20Donnelly%20Training%20Area%2C%20Alaska%2C%20Feb.%208%2C%202024.%3Cp%3EU.S.%20Army%20photo%20by%20Sgt.%20Keon%20Horton%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20are%20training%20to%20become%20a%20jumpmaster%2C%20there%20is%20a%20very%20high%20standard%20for%20what%20you%20need%20to%20do%20at%20the%20schoolhouse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInspecting%20paratroopers%20before%20a%20jump%20%E2%80%94%20when%20you're%20meticulously%20going%20item%20by%20item%20on%20each