ce-index-2024-5%23%3A~%3Atext%3DUS%2520inflation%2520saw%2520some%2520moderation%2520in%2520April.%26amp%3Btext%3DInflation%2520in%2520the%2520US%2520is%2C2023%2520to%2520this%2520past%2520April.%5C%22%3Ecooler%20April%20inflation%20reading%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rally%20in%20itself%20is%20problematic%20for%20stocks%2C%20he%20warned%2C%20as%20they're%20already%20so%20expensive%20that%20it's%20hard%20to%20imagine%20the%20market%20moving%20higher%20from%20here.%20He%20sees%20the%20benchmark%20index%20being%20prone%20to%20multiple%20sharp%20corrections%20of%20at%20least%2010%25%2C%20ending%20the%20year%20around%204%2C500.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20next%20move%20will%20be%20down%2C%20rather%20than%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20Morrison%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20view%20puts%20him%20at%20odds%20with%20the%20growing%20number%20of%20bulls%20in%20the%20market%20who%20see%20an%20eventual%20rate%20cut%20from%20the%20Federal%20Reserve%20as%20a%20strong%20positive%20catalyst.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Morrison%20thinks%20the%20Fed's%20first%20rate%20cut%20could%20easily%20be%20postponed%20another%20three%20months%E2%80%94meaning%20no%20cut%20this%20summer%20or%20possibly%20no%20cuts%20at%20all%20this%20year.%20All%20it%20would%20take%20is%20one%20hot%20inflation%20reading%20to%20dash%20the%20prospect%20of%20Fed%20rate%20cuts%20this%20year%20altogether%2C%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInvestors%20are%20suffering%20from%20a%20large%20dose%20of%20FOMO%2C%20and%20I'm%20concerned%20that%20we%20could%20be%20in%20the%20process%20of%20a%20blow-off%20top%20with%20echoes%20of%20the%20moves%20seen%20back%20in%20early%202020%2C%26quot%3B%20Morrison%20told%20BI%2C%20pointing%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feconomic-outlook-pandemic-stock-market-crash-inflation-recession-rates-ai-2024-2%23%3A~%3Atext%3DFrightened%2520investors%2520dumped%2520stocks%2520in%2C10%2525%2520for%2520four%2520consecutive%2520months.%5C%