chrader-oh-canada-jacob-elordi-jockstrap-scene-1236008241%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20was%20skeptical%20about%20introducing%20video%20games%20to%20my%203%20young%20kids.%20I%20found%20an%20option%20that%20keeps%20them%20moving%20while%20playing.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Girl%20playing%20Peppa%20Pig%20Game%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66461c6820abc1efe8fa6c45%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author's%20kids%20are%20engaged%20while%20playing%20with%20Nex%20Playground%20and%20it%20keeps%20them%20moving.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EI%20have%20three%20kids%20under%20the%20age%20of%207.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMy%20oldest%20had%20been%20asking%20us%20if%20he%20could%20start%20playing%20video%20games.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI%20didn't%20like%20the%20idea%20of%20them%20being%20sedentary%2C%20but%20found%20Nex%20Playground%20keeps%20them%20moving.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EI%20grew%20up%20in%20the%20late%2080s%20and%2090s%20and%20was%20an%20avid%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-nintendo-games-of-all-time-based-on-critics-reviews-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENintendo%20player%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20had%20the%20NES%20in%20my%20room%20and%20pretty%20much%20unlimited%20time%20with%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20became%20a%20parent%2C%20I%20realized%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-screen-time-expert-limits-kids-screen-time-use-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etoo%20much%20screen%20time%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20not%20good%20for%20my%20kids'%20developing%20brains.%20Also%2C%20I%20felt%20like%20they%20needed%20to%20move%20more%20after%20spending%20all%20day%20sitting%20in%20school%2C%20even%20though%20they%20were%20still%20on%20the%20younger%20side%20for%20organized%20sports.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20my%20oldest%2C%20aged%206%2C%20kept%20asking%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffallout-review-amazon-prime-video-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplay%20video%20games%3C%2Fa%3E%20because%20all%20his%20friends%20were%20already%20doing%20it.%20Thankfully%2C%20I%20found%20a%20solution%20that%20scratches%20his%20itch%20for%20playing%20and%20doesn't%20make%20me%20feel%20guilty%20about%20screen%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f248633c-38c1-41fe-9ce9-2c4270aa1483%5C%22%3EA%20video%20game%20system%20that%20gets%20kids%20moving%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20felt%20a%20little%20hypocritical%20for%20not%20allowing%20my%20son%20to%20play%20video%20games%20after%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20spent%20so%20much%20time%20doing%20so%20growing%20up.%20But%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20I%20felt%20like%20adding%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fscreen-free-family-meals-kids-entertainment-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emore%20screen%20time%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20not%20really%20going%20to%20benefit%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20recommended%20that%20kids%20under%206%20don't%20get%20more%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fhow-much-screen-time-is-too-much%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethan%20an%20hour%20a%20day%20of%20screen%20time%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20weekdays.%20But%2C%20as%20most%20parents%20know%2C%20it's%20so%20hard%20to%20negotiate%20with%20kids%20when%20it's%20time%20to%20put%20an%20end%20to%20their%20favorite%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20heard%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplayground.nex.inc%2Fproducts%2Fnex-playground%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENex%20Playground%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20was%20intrigued.%20The%20concept%20is%20pretty%20simple%20and%20similar%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkinect-was-not-microsofts-fault-2015-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5