%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecoworkers%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20then%20became%20friends%2C%20and%20now%2C%20we%20have%20been%20a%20couple%20for%2011%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e716e54d-e827-46b5-9f41-142325c88b33%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20bonded%20in%20and%20out%20of%20the%20office%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe'd%20play%20silly%20games%20to%20distract%20ourselves%20from%20the%20awfulness.%20One%20was%20called%20%26quot%3BWould%20you%20rather%3F%26quot%3B%20We'd%20ask%20each%20other%20things%20like%3A%20%26quot%3BWould%20you%20rather%20eat%20a%20newborn%20baby%20or%20get%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgonorrhea-syphilis-cases-out-of-control-in-us-std-expert-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esexually%20transmitted%20disease%3C%2Fa%3E%3F%26quot%3B%20It%20was%20really%20stupid%20stuff%2C%20but%20we'd%20giggle%20when%20we%20should've%20been%20working.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20had%20the%20same%20group%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworried-lose-work-friends-quit-job-closer-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eoffice%20friends%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20they%20were%20flaky.%20We'd%20arrange%20dinners%2C%20movies%2C%20or%20after-work%20drinks.%20But%20one%20by%20one%2C%20they'd%20all%20bail%20at%20the%20last%20minute%2C%20leaving%20just%20Tim%20and%20me.%20Tim%20proved%20to%20me%20then%20that%20he%20was%20reliable%3B%20he'd%20show%20up%20when%20he%20said%20he%20would.%20And%20so%20would%20I.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOften%20it%20was%20just%20Tim%20and%20I%20alone%20%E2%80%94%20even%20though%20we%20both%20were%20in%20relationships%20at%20the%20time.%20I%20initially%20saw%20Tim%20just%20as%20a%20friend.%20I%20didn't%20have%20any%20romantic%20hopes%20or%20ideas%20for%20the%20first%20few%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20then%20Tim's%20relationship%20ended.%20He%20discovered%20his%20partner%20was%20having%20an%20affair.%20Meanwhile%2C%20I%20was%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.busine