ring%20the%20next%20five%20days%2C%20and%20heat%20wave%20conditions%20will%20persist%20over%20central%20and%20east%20India%20over%20the%20next%20three%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWarm%20winds%20and%20high%20temperatures%20have%20swept%20north%20India.%20Delhi's%20Najafgarh%20was%20the%20warmest%20place%20in%20the%20country%20after%2047.6%20degrees%20Celsius%20was%20recorded%20yesterday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajasthan%2C%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20are%20marked%20in%20red%20in%20the%20India%20Meteorological%20Department's%20alert%2C%20asking%20people%20and%20authorities%20to%20take%20action.%20Meanwhile%2C%20parts%20of%20eastern%20Rajasthan%20and%20western%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20are%20in%20orange%20and%20people%20have%20been%20advised%20to%20stay%20alert%20and%20be%20prepared%20for%20high%20temperatures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EHeavy%20to%20very%20heavy%20rainfall%20very%20likely%20to%20continue%20over%20south%20Peninsular%20India%20till%2023rd%20with%20extremely%20heavy%20falls%20during%2019-21%20May%2C%202024.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FywcueEWW4C%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FywcueEWW4C%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20India%20Meteorological%20Department%20(%40Indiametdept)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FIndiametdept%2Fstatus%2F1791746612450193497%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMay%2018%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mercury%20breached%2045%20degrees%20Celsius%20at%2019%20places%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%2018%20in%20Haryana%2C%20eight%20in%20Delhi%20and%20two%20in%20Punjab.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20threshold%20for%20a%20heat%20wave%20is%20met%20when%20the%20maximum%20temperature%20of%20a%20weather%20station%20reaches%20at%20least%2040%20degrees%20Celsius%20in%20the%20plains%2C%2037%20degrees%20in%20the%20coastal%20areas%2C%20and%2030%20degrees%20in%20the%20hilly%20regions%2C%20and%20the%20departure%20from%20normal%20is%20at%20least%204.5%20notches.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20severe%20heat%20wave%20is%20declared%20if%20the%20departure%20from%20normal%20exceeds%206.4%20notches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20temperature%20is%20expected%20to%20stay%20in%20the%20normal%20range%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20Ladakh%20and%20Himachal%20Pradesh.%20Hot%20and%20humid%20conditions%20are%20expected%20in%20Uttarakhand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20in%20southern%20India%2C%20a%20heavy%20to%20heavy%20rainfall%20alert%20has%20been%20issued%20till%20the%2023rd%2C%20with%20extremely%20heavy%20falls%20during%2019-21%20May.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20weather%20office%20said%20the%20southwest%20monsoon%20is%20very%20likely%20to%20advance%20into%20the%20south%20Andaman%20Sea%2C%20some%20parts%20of%20the%20Southeast%20Bay%20of%20Bengal%20and%20Nicobar%20Islands%20around%20May%2019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20a%20group%20of%20leading%20climate%20scientists%20said%20similar%20heat%20waves%20could%20occur%20once%20every%2030%20years%2C%20and%20these%20have%20already%20become%20about%2045%20times%20more%20likely%20due%20to%20climate%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20scientists%20from%20the%20World%20Weather%20Attribution%20group%20emphasised%20that%20heat%20waves%20intensified%20by%20climate%20change%20are%20making%20life%20much%20tougher%20for%20people%20living%20in%20poverty%20across%20Asia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IMD%20had%20earlier%20warned%20of%20extreme%20heat%20in%20India%20during%20the%20April-June%20period%2C%20coinciding%20with%20the%20seven-phase%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20that%20end%20on%20June%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716028800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fra3q26oo_heatwave-ians_625x300_06_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fheatwave-warning-for-northwest-india-temperatures-to-stay-over-40-degrees-5691499%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20weather%20department%2