20to%20vote%20from%20home%2C%20the%20CEO%20office%20said.%20%26quot%3BFormer%20prime%20minister%20Dr%20Manmohan%20Singh%20and%20former%20Union%20minister%20Dr%20Murli%20Manohar%20Joshi%20successfully%20cast%20their%20votes%20on%20May%2017%20from%20their%20home%20availing%20home%20voting%20facility%20in%20the%20New%20Delhi%20parliamentary%20constituency%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20office%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20vice%20president%20Mohammad%20Hamid%20Ansari%20cast%20his%20vote%20on%20Thursday%2C%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20deputy%20prime%20minister%20LK%20Advani%20cast%20his%20vote%20on%20Saturday%2C%20sources%20said.%20On%20the%20first%20day%2C%201%2C482%20voters%20exercised%20their%20franchise%20from%20home.%20A%20total%20of%205%2C406%20voters%20across%20Delhi%20--%20elderly%20individuals%20and%20PwDs%20--%20have%20filled%20out%20Form%2012D%20to%20avail%20of%20the%20home%20voting%20facility%20in%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20initiative%20ensures%20these%20voters%20can%20participate%20in%20the%20electoral%20process%20with%20ease%20and%20dignity%2C%20eliminating%20the%20need%20to%20visit%20polling%20stations.%20Delhi%20will%20go%20to%20polls%20on%20May%2025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716026940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F2v4buk88_vote-from-home_625x300_18_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fformer-pm-manmohan-singh-lk-advani-cast-votes-using-home-voting-facility-5691159%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20vice%20president%20Mohammad%20Hamid%20Ansari%2C%20former%20prime%20minister%20Dr%20Manmohan%20Singh%2C%20former%20deputy%20prime%20minister%20LK%20Advani%20and%20former%20Union%20minister%20Dr%20Murli%20Manohar%20Joshi%20have%20cast%20their%20vote