uot%3BWhen%20Virat%20Kohli%20started%20his%20career%2C%20it%20was%20a%20stop-start%20career.%20The%20fact%20that%20MS%20Dhoni%20gave%20him%20that%20little%20extra%20momentum%20is%20why%20he%20is%20the%20Kohli%20we%20see%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20Gavaskar%20said%20on%20Star%20Sports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGavaskar%20has%20been%20critical%20of%20Kohli's%20form%20this%20season%20and%20also%20slammed%20the%20RCB%20icon%20over%20his%20outburst%20on%20criticism%20over%20his%20strike-rate%20during%20the%20initial%20phase%20of%20IPL%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKohli%20had%20taken%20a%20swipe%20at%20his%20critics%2C%20saying%3A%20%26quot%3BAll%20the%20people%20who%20talk%20about%20strike%20rates%20and%20me%20not%20playing%20spin%20well%20are%20the%20ones%20who%20love%20talking%20about%20this%20stuff.%20But%20for%20me%2C%20it's%20just%20about%20winning%20the%20game%20for%20the%20team.%20And%20there's%20a%20reason%20why%20you%20do%20it%20for%2015%20years%20-%20because%20you've%20done%20this%20day%20in%20%5Band%5D%20day%20out%3B%20you've%20won%20games%20for%20your%20teams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20not%20quite%20sure%20if%20you've%20been%20in%20that%20situation%20yourself%20to%20sit%20and%20speak%20about%20the%20game%20from%20a%20box.%20I%20don't%20really%20think%20it's%20the%20same%20thing%20%5Bas%20playing%20out%20there%5D.%20So%20for%20me%2C%20it's%20just%20about%20doing%20my%20job.%20People%20can%20talk%20about%20their%20own%20ideas%20and%20assumptions%20of%20the%20game%2C%20but%20those%20who%20have%20done%20it%20day%20in%20%5Band%5D%20day%20out%20know%20what's%20happening%2C%20and%20it's%20kind%20of%20a%20muscle%20memory%20for%20me%20now.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20Kohli's%20remark%2C%20Gavaskar%20came%20up%20with%20a%20sharp%20retort%2C%20saying%3A%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20have%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20118%2C%20you%20come%20and%20face%20the%20first%20ball%2C%20and%20then%20you%20get%20out%20in%20the%2014th%20or%2015th%20over%20and%20your%20strike%20rate%20is%20118%20-%20if%20you%20want%20applause%20for%20that%2C%20then%20that's%20a%20little%20bit%20different.%20We've%20all%20played%20a%20bit%20of%20cricket%2C%20not%20a%20lot%20of%20cricket%2C%20but%20we%20speak%20about%20what%20we%20see.%20We%20don't%20necessarily%20have%20any%20likes%20and%20dislikes.%20Even%20if%20we%20have%20likes%20or%20dislikes%2C%20we%20actually%20speak%20about%20what's%20happening.%20So%2C%20I%20would%20be%20very%20disappointed%20if%20Star%20Sports%20showed%20this%20once%20more%20because%20that%20would%20be%20questioning%20all%20of%20us%20commentators.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20all%20the%20criticism%20from%20Gavaskar%20and%20a%20few%20others%2C%20Kohli%20continues%20to%20pile%20up%20runs%20in%20IPL%202024.%20He%20is%20currently%20the%20leading%20run-getter%20in%20the%20tournament%20with%20661%20runs%20at%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20155.16%20from%2013%20matches.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716025920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-05%2Fan497fso_virat-kohli-ms-dhoni-afp_625x300_14_May_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Fvirat-kohli-we-see-today-is-because-of-ms-dhoni-sunil-gavaskars-stunning-statement-5689580%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sunil%20Gavaskar%20has%20been%20critical%20of%20Virat%20Kohli's%20form%20this%20season%20and%20also%20slammed%20the%20RCB%20icon%20over%20his%20outburst%20on%20criticism%20over%20his%20strike-rate%20during%20the%20initial%20phase%20of%20IPL%202024.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Fvirat-kohli-we-see-today-is-because-of-ms-dhoni-sunil-gavaskars-stunning-statement-5689580%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Fvirat-kohli-we-see-today-is-because-of-ms-dhoni-sunil-gavaskars-stunning-statement-5689580%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fip