ith%20the%20speed%20of%20an%20American%20football%20player%E2%80%9D%20to%20prevent%20it%20from%20being%20passed.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn-%3E%20That%20should%20just%20be%20an%20official%20process%20in%20any%20democracy.%20Love%20it%20%E2%80%A6%20haha%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F0C4T4DbbSU%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F0C4T4DbbSU%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Lord%20Bebo%20(%40MyLordBebo)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMyLordBebo%2Fstatus%2F1791558207996895335%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMay%2017%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20incident%20occurred%20just%20days%20before%20President-elect%20Lai%20Ching-te%20is%20set%20to%20take%20office%20on%20Monday%2C%20having%20won%20January's%20election%20even%20though%20his%20Democratic%20Progressive%20Party%20(DPP)%20does%20not%20have%20a%20majority%20in%20the%20legislature%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fasia-pacific%2Ftaiwan-lawmakers-exchange-blows-bitter-dispute-over-parliament-reforms-2024-05-17%2F%C2%A0%5C%22%3EReuters%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EKuomintang%20(KMT)%2C%20the%20primary%20opposition%20party%2C%20has%20more%20seats%20than%20the%20DPP%20but%20not%20enough%20to%20control%20the%20parliament%20alone.%20So%2C%20they%20are%20teaming%20up%20with%20the%20smaller%20Taiwan%20People's%20Party%20(TPP)%20to%20push%20for%20their%20common%20goals.%20The%20opposition%20wants%20to%20give%20parliament%20more%20power%20to%20check%20the%20government's%20actions%2C%20including%20a%20controversial%20plan%20to%20punish%20officials%20who%20lie%20in%20parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EEven%20before%20the%20votes%20were%20cast%2C%20some%20lawmakers%20screamed%20and%20shoved%20each%20other%20outside%20the%20legislative%20chamber.%20Later%2C%20the%20parliament%20floor%20saw%20chaos%20as%20lawmakers%20turned%20to%20the%20Speaker's%20seat%2C%20jum