0trek%20to%20the%20Valley%20of%20Flowers%20in%20Uttarakhand%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20important%20to%20consider%20the%20most%20convenient%20modes%20of%20transportation%20to%20reach%20your%20starting%20point%20at%20Govindghat.%20Here%E2%80%99s%20how%20you%20can%20get%20there%20%E2%80%93%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBy%20Car%3A%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20drive%20from%20major%20cities%20like%20Delhi%20or%20Dehradun%20to%20Govindghat.%20The%20journey%20from%20Delhi%20takes%20approximately%2010-12%20hours%2C%20depending%20on%20traffic%20and%20road%20conditions.%20From%20Delhi%2C%20you%20can%20also%20avail%20public%20transport%20from%20ISBT%20or%20Delhi%20Gate%20to%20Rishikesh%20and%20take%20another%20bus%20to%20Joshimath%20and%20then%20to%20Govindghat.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%E2%80%99ll%20travel%20through%20major%20towns%20such%20as%20Rishikesh%20and%20Haridwar%20before%20reaching%20Govindghat.%20The%20roads%20are%20scenic%2C%20offering%20beautiful%20views%20of%20the%20mountains%20and%20rivers%20along%20the%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBy%20Air%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20nearest%20airport%20to%20Govindghat%20is%20Jolly%20Grant%20Airport%20in%20Dehradun.%20From%20the%20airport%2C%20you%20can%20hire%20a%20taxi%20or%20take%20a%20bus%20to%20Govindghat.%20The%20drive%20from%20Dehradun%20to%20Govindghat%20is%20286%20km%20and%20takes%20approximately%2010-12%20hours%2C%20so%20you%20might%20want%20to%20plan%20your%20flight%20arrival%20time%20accordingly.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EYou%20can%20opt%20for%20public%20transport%20from%20Dehradun%20to%20Rishikesh%20and%20then%20to%20Joshimath%20and%20so%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC6pxBHnySgj%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%