0who%20travelled%20to%20the%20Valley%20of%20Flowers%20in%202019.%20The%20couple%20completed%20the%20trek%20in%205%20days%2C%20slowly%20taking%20in%20the%20natural%20beauty%20of%20the%20landscapes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20their%20day-wise%20plan-%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDay%201%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20couple%20drove%20from%20Rishikesh%20to%20Joshimath.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20reached%20Joshimath%20in%20the%20evening%20and%20checked%20into%20a%20local%20guest%20house%20to%20recharge%20ourselves%20for%20the%20upcoming%20trek%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20shared.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDay%202%3A%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fstrong%3EWe%20trekked%20till%20Ghangharia%20which%20is%20around%209%20km%20from%20the%20starting%20point%20and%20is%20at%20an%20altitude%20of%20around%2010%2C000%20ft.%20We%20stayed%20overnight%20at%20a%20campsite%20in%20Ghangharia.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20village%20serves%20as%20the%20base%20camp%20for%20the%20Valley%20of%20Flowers%20and%20has%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F298559%2Fbest-jungle-camps-wildlife-safaris-india-for-nature-lovers-travel-long-weekend%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evarious%20stay%20options%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20eateries%20and%20scenic%20views%2C%20making%20it%20an%20ideal%20place%20to%20rest%20and%20recharge%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20hike.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20960px)%20100vw%2C%20960px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-05-17-at-12.34.12-PM-1715929564.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Himani%20and%20Sagar%20Patel.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-05-17-at-12.34.12-PM-1715929564.jpeg%20960w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhats