%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBefore%20I%20planted%20the%20avocado%20plants%2C%20they%20were%20kept%20in%20the%20nursery%20until%202023.%20Finally%2C%20in%20March%202023%2C%20I%20planted%20them%20in%20the%20fields.%20This%20will%20be%20the%20first%20year%20the%20crop%20will%20be%20commercially%20viable%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarshit%20now%20sells%20avocado%20plants%20all%20over%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarshit%20says%20that%20he%20uses%20Israeli%20technology%20to%20irrigate%20his%20plants.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20employ%20advanced%20techniques%20that%20allow%20us%20to%20control%20water%20distribution%20precisely%20to%20the%20root%20zone%20of%20each%20plant.%20Instead%20of%20using%20flood%20irrigation%2C%20which%20wastes%20a%20significant%20amount%20of%20water%2C%20we%20ensure%20that%20each%20plant%20receives%20the%20exact%20amount%20of%20water%20and%20fertiliser%20it%20needs%20every%20day.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETherefore%2C%20regardless%20of%20the%20topography%20of%20the%20orchard%2C%20you%20will%20have%20an%20even%20distribution%20of%20water%20for%20each%20and%20every%20plan%2C%20he%20stresses.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETips%20for%20new%20urban%20farmers%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20planting%20avocados%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20important%20to%20keep%20a%20few%20things%20in%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarshit%20says%20that%20you%20need%20a%20reliable%20water%20source%20or%20should%20practise%20rainwater%20harvesting%2C%20especially%20if%20you%E2%80%99re%20in%20hot%20climatic%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20regions%20like%20the%20Northeast%2C%20natural%20rainwater%20is%20usually%20sufficient.%20For%20other%20areas%20like%20Punjab%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20or%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20a%20dependable%20water%20source%20is%20crucial%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20key%20consideration%20is%20choosing%20the%20right%20variety%20of%20avocado%20plants.%2