then%20grafted%2C%20leading%20to%20variability%20in%20quality.%20My%20plants%2C%20which%20cost%20Rs%202%2C500%20each%2C%20are%20grown%20on%20commercial%20rootstocks%20of%20specific%20avocados%20developed%20in%20Israel%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAvocado%20plants%20consist%20of%20two%20parts%3A%20the%20rootstock%20(the%20part%20below%20the%20graft)%20and%20the%20cultivar.%20The%20rootstock%20imparts%20certain%20properties%20to%20the%20entire%20plant%2C%20such%20as%20high%20yield%20and%20manageable%20canopy%20size.%20This%20allows%20for%20easier%20harvesting%20at%20heights%20of%20just%2010%20to%2012%20feet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChoosing%20the%20right%20rootstock%20and%20variety%2C%20as%20well%20as%20seeking%20the%20appropriate%20support%2C%20is%20essential.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRemember%2C%20different%20climates%20require%20different%20management%20practices%20and%20techniques.%20For%20instance%2C%20the%20methods%20used%20in%20South%20India%20differ%20from%20those%20used%20in%20Central%20India%20where%20I%20am%20based.%20Expecting%20similar%20results%20from%20cheaper%20plants%20without%20considering%20these%20factors%20may%20lead%20to%20disappointment%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3B%20All%20Pictures%20Credit%3A%20Harshit%20Godha)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715777750000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Favocado-1-1715758265.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D350000%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Urban%20farmer%20Harshit%20Godha%20took%20inspiration%20from%20Israeli%20farmers%20growing%20avocadoes%20and%20has%20successfully%20grown%20the%20fruit%20in%20India.%20He%20shares%20how%20you%20can%20grow%20them%20too.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F350000%2Fhow-to-grow-avocado-in-india-urban-farmer-harshit-godha-imports-saplings-from-israel-teaches-farming%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22From%202%20Cr%20Salary%20to%202%20Million%20Followers%3A%20How%20%E2%80%98FoodPharmer%E2%80%99%20Started%20A%20Food%20Revolution%20in%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20grab%20a%20food%20item%20at%20the%20grocery%20store%2C%20our%20instinct%20is%20often%20to%20check%20the%20expiry%20date.%20But%20do%20we%20also%20spare%20just%20a%20couple%20more%20minutes%20to%20scan%20the%20ingredient%20list%3F%20These%20extra%20moments%20could%20be%20crucial%2C%20shaping%20our%20understanding%20of%20the%20food%20we%E2%80%99re%20putting%20into%20our%20bodies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPackaged%20food%20has%20become%20integral%20to%20our%20lives%2C%20whether%20we%20like%20it%20or%20not.%20Therefore%2C%20making%20conscious%20decisions%20to%20opt%20for%20packaged%20foods%20that%20won%E2%80%99t%20pose%20additional%20risks%20is%20essential.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20small%20step%2C%20but%20it%20can%20have%20a%20significant%20impact%20on%20our%20health%20and%20well-being.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecent%20reports%20have%20emphasised%20the%20critical%20importance%20of%20carefully%20reading%20food%20labels.%20The%20Indian%20Council%20of%20Medical%20Research%20(ICMR)%20released%20dietary%20guidelines%20for%20Indians%20on%20May%208%2C%20cautioning%20that%20the%20information%20provided%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F348030%2Fmdh-everest-sambhar-masala-fssai-guidelines-food-safety-ethylene-oxide-fish-curry-masala-singapore-hong-kong%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epackaged%20food%20labels%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20often%20be%20misleading.%20%E2%80%9CHealth%20claims%20on%20packaged%20food%20are%20designed%20to%20catch%20the%20consumer%E2%80%99s%20attention%20and%20convince%20them%20that%20the%20product%20is%20healthy.%20Always%20read%20food%20label%20information%20to%20know%20about%20the%20contents%20inside%20the%20pack%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20guidelines%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDon%E2%80%99t%20be%20fooled%20by%20labels%20like%20%E2%80%98healthy%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98no%20sugar%20added%E2%80%99.%20One%20man%20who%20has%20been%20trying%20to%20decode%20these%20food%20labels%20and%20teach%20Indians%20how%20to%20read%20them%20is%20Revant%20Himatsingka%20aka%20%E2%80%98foodpharmer%E2%80%99%20on%20Instagram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20past%20year%2C%20this%2032-year-old%20has%20been%20leading%20the%20charge%20in%20promoting%20health%20literacy%20and%20raising%20awareness%20about%20the%20importance%20of%20reading%20food%20labels%20before%20making%20purchases.%20Through%20his%20Instagram%20page%2C%20he%20has%20gathered%20a%20following%20of%20over%202.2%20million%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20left%20behind%20a%20lucrative%20Rs%202%20crore%20job%20on%20Wall%20Street%2C%20this%20certified%20health%20coach%20is%20on%20a%20mission%20to%20spark%20a%20%E2%80%9Chealth%20revolution%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIndians%20are%20educated%20but%20not%20health%20literate.%20I%E2%80%99m%20therefore%20focusing%20on%20health%20literacy%2C%20with%20my%20major%20target%20being%20children.%20You%20should%20develop%20healthy%20habits%20in%20children%20from%20day%20one%20and%20keep%20them%20away%20from%20junk%20to%20reduce%20the%20likelihood%20of%20developing%20health%20issues%20later%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Revant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHolding%20large%20FMCG%20conglomerates%20accountable%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGrowing%20up%20in%20a%2090s%20Kolkata%2C%20Revant%20had%20a%20regular%20childhood%2C%20which%20included%20biscuits%2C%20packaged%20foods%2C%20and%20drinks%20like%20Bournvita.%20The%20young%20boy%20was%20then%20blissfully%20unaware%20of%20the%20harmful%20effects%20of%20the%20food%20he%20consumed%2C%20like%20millions%20of%20Indians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-b