rstanding%20food%20labels.%20With%20this%20plan%20in%20place%2C%20he%20quit%20his%20job%20and%20returned%20to%20India%2C%20much%20to%20the%20chagrin%20of%20his%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20he%20was%20clear%20about%20his%20mission%20and%20took%20on%20the%20baton%20of%20teaching%20Indians%20what%20he%20calls%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20most%20important%20life%20skill%E2%80%9D.%20His%20problem%20lies%20with%20packaged%20food%20that%20masquerades%20as%20healthy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20April%202023%2C%20he%20kicked%20off%20his%20stint%20as%20%E2%80%98Foodpharmer%E2%80%99%20with%20a%20video%20about%20Bournvita%2C%20manufactured%20by%20Mondelez.%20The%20video%20highlighted%20the%20excessive%20amount%20of%20sugar%20in%20the%20drink%2C%20yet%20calling%20itself%20%E2%80%98healthy%E2%80%99%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20could%20cause%20diabetes.%20The%20video%20went%20viral%20across%20social%20media%20platforms%2C%20leading%20to%20legal%20trouble%20for%20the%20former%20consultant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMondelez%20sent%20him%20a%20legal%20notice%20asking%20him%20to%20take%20down%20the%20video.%20Left%20with%20no%20choice%2C%20Revant%20took%20it%20down%20and%20issued%20a%20statement.%20However%2C%20he%20had%20achieved%20what%20he%20set%20out%20to%20do%20%E2%80%94%20create%20awareness%20among%20Indians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EStay%20away%20from%20sugary%20drinks%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20legal%20notice%2C%20Cadbury%20reduced%20the%20quantity%20of%20added%20sugar%20in%20Bournvita%20by%2014.4%20percent%20in%20December%202023%2C%20validating%20the%20content%20creator%E2%80%99s%20efforts.%20The%20Central%20Government%20also%20directed%20e-commerce%20firms%20to%20remove%20Bournvita%20and%20other%20such%20drinks%20from%20the%20health%20drinks%20category.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20major%20product%20that%20reduced%20its%20sugar%20content%20by%2022%20percent%20was%20%E2%80%98Maggi%20rich%20tomato%20ketchup%E2%80%99.%20Revant%20made%20a%20vi