isting%20line%2C%20just%20draw%20a%20bigger%20line%20next%20to%20it.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20this%20end%2C%20Chaturvedi%20learnt%20early%20on%20that%20the%20only%20way%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20plant%20species%20of%20Uttarakhand%20thrived%20despite%20all%20odds%20was%20to%20ensure%20their%20propagation%20was%20amped%20up.%20%E2%80%9CSince%20day%20one%2C%20we%20have%20made%20it%20our%20motto%20that%20if%20there%20are%20100%20plants%20in%20the%20initial%20habitat%2C%20we%20will%20grow%20500%20in%20our%20centres.%E2%80%9D%20Currently%2C%202%2C200%20endemic%20plant%20species%20are%20being%20conserved%20across%20the%20forest%20wing%E2%80%99s%20seven%20centres.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fplant-conservation-2-1715250601.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Tamil%20Palm%20is%20one%20of%20the%20few%20species%20that%20can%20survive%20in%20frost%20and%20snow%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fplant-conservation-2-1715250601.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fplant-conservation-2-1715250601-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fplant-conservation-2-1715250601-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fplant-conservation-2-1715250601-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fplant-conservation-2-1715250601-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-349430%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20Tamil%20Palm%20is%20one%20of%20the%20few%20species%20that%20can%20survive%20in%20frost%20and%20snow%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Chaturvedi%